headline: Williams Companies Raises 2026 Outlook And Dividend As Projects Advance
summary: Williams Companies (NYSE:WMB) issued an updated 2026 adjusted earnings forecast that sits above current consensus expectations. The company also announced a 5% dividend increase, supported by new pipeline and offshore project growth. The updates highlight the role of recently completed and upcoming infrastructure projects in Williams Companies' medium term plans.
